title: The O.J. Howard Redemption Episode | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
We highlight the Week 10 players you should spend the big bucks on, headlined by Christian McCaffrey, before we give our overrated and middle-range sweet-spot picks (1:45). Then, we tell you why it somehow makes sense to start O.J. Howard, Kalen Ballage, and Daniel Jones this week before building our Week 10 daily fantasy lineup (21:45).
Hosts: Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck
